title: SUMMER OF HEALING…WE THINK?
description: In true Gals fashion, Charlotte is trying every new health practice under the sun from Reiki to breathwork with some psychics to top it off. Additionally, the Gals share their new relationship with alcohol and how they’ve noticed the changes in NYC.
dc:creator: Gimlet Gals
